# THE PRIVACY FLOOR — Tight Spiral Productions
# Written 2026-07-14, after finding 18 faculty emails and 7 named students
# live on the public internet for at least 48 hours.
#
# EVERY FILE IN THIS REPO IS A PUBLIC URL. There is no other tier.
# GitHub Pages serves the whole tree. A file pushed here is a file published.
#
# This ignore list is the ONLY thing standing between a working file and
# publication. It is a floor, not a suggestion.

